name: HPxLOTM: A Wizard's Path to Divinity
summary: Transmigrating once was already a life-changing, earth-shattering experience. But TWICE?That was the question Edward was left asking when he suddenly stumbled upon a garden with a crimson moon hanging in the night sky while taking a leisurely stroll through Hogwarts.Reborn in 1980s Englandspecifically, the magical world of Harry PotterEdward thought he had hit the jackpot.Fast forward three years, he had settled into Hogwarts life, dabbling in magic, and maybejust maybeleaning a little too far into Definitely-Not-Dark Arts. Then, one fateful night, while experimenting in the Room of Requirement, he found himself in a world where knowing too much doesnt just get you killed.It leads to something far worse.And unfortunately, Edward knew way too much.Shit.What followed was pure chaos. A nobles mansion went up in flames, his daughter got abducted (a misunderstanding, really), and to top it all off, Edward realized he wasnt stuckhe would be travelling between both worlds at regular intervals.At that point, he had enough."To hell with the plot!"A Harry Potter x Lord of the Mysteries fic.You can read upto 40 Advanced Chapters!Link - (p)atreon(.com)/Iseeblack[Remove the Parentheses]
